snippet.title: In Amber - Ember Heart (Official Audio)
snippet.description:
"Ember Heart" is a song from the debut album Human of the Bulgarian Hard Rock band In Amber. The song is composed by Vladislav Vergilov. The text is written by Vladislav Vergilov.

In Amber is a Melodic/Hard Rock band from Bulgaria. 

Band members:
Emiliyan Velizarov - Vocals and Guitars
Vladislav Vergilov - Lead Guitars
Georgi Uzunov - Bass Guitars

Ember Heart

Out in the cold there is a fire, burning inside my heart!
There is a secret desire, crawling inside my mind!
All of the choices we’re making, led by the flames of passion.
We realize that we are falling, drowned in the sweet obsession.

Feel the beat, feel the heat
Look inside - 
inside my burning heart.
The bittersweet, the overheat
Come inside -
inside my ember heart.

Out on the streets there is an impulse, driving us all to the edge!
We know we “will live forever” - this is our dearest pledge!
We’re not afraid of the Unknown, we all pursue our dreams.
There is a common distraction. Nothing is like what it seems…

No! We are the chosen ones forever!
Now! We could be living now or never!

Feel the beat, feel the heat
Look inside - 
inside my burning heart.
The bittersweet, the overheat
Come inside -
inside my ember heart.
